value: India to SE Asia; winters to Greater Sundas

Southeastern Asia from Garhwal, the Himalayas, Assam and the lower Yangtse valley, south over India, Burma, Malay Peninsula and Indo- china; Ceylon, Sumatra, Lingga Archipelago, Java and Borneo; straggler to the Philippines and Celebes. Occurs in China only as a summer resident.
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World
